<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5> drive someone to the wall • drive someone up the wall</xh5><p> <i>drive someone to the wall—</i>push a person to the last extremity: He complained that the company was being <u>driven to the wall</u> by the workers’ demands for higher wages.</p><p><i>drive someone up the wall—</i>make smb. very angry or mentally confused: Someone is running a jackhammer outside of my office and it’s <u>driving me up the wall</u>.</p></entry>
